### You have the option of changing the log level

1. Go to: [build.gradle](./build.gradle) file

2. Add `simulation` closure with the desired log level (`DEBUG` / `INFO` / `WARN` / `ERR`)
```groovy
simulation {
   logLevel = "DEBUG"
}
```